乜分別？&hellip;</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n精神科醫生話你有病就係有病<br />\n無科學根據架<br />\n亂寫假紙係明知病人無病<br />\n有醫療紀錄"},{"pid":"35d59492efc2dd78ebdc43188173801700ef4fa1","tid":94828,"uid":35089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T11:21:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\">許龍杰接受《香港01》查詢時表示，基於病人的私隱問題，未有再透露個案詳情。許曾表示，名校學生服食ADHD藥物比例較高，源自家長分享，並未有客觀數據。 <br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n勿跟車太貼</blockquote><br />\nADHD 條車龍過咗太平洋囉喎 <br />\nOverdiagnosis同undertreatment同時存</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nADHD 亂開藥個問題有左好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n美國d 個案都升左好多，但比人質疑係咪真有此病，有本書叫 ADHD Does Not Exist講呢個問題<br />\n不過香港01真係好垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9891398815d0f95cc0cad01196c354cf3e8bdcb","tid":94828,"uid":2192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T11:28:06.000Z","msg":"香港01又製造恐慌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}